      "title": "2. The enclosed Master Direction incorporates updated guidelines / circulars on the",
      "text": "2. The enclosed Master Direction incorporates updated guidelines / circulars on the\nsubject.\nYours faithfully,\n(Sanjeev Prakash) Chief General Manager-In-Charge\nEncl: As above\n_______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________\nमुद्रा प्रबंध िवभाग, केंद्रीय कायार्लय, चौथी मंिजल, अमर भवन, सर पी .एम .रोड, मुंबई - 400 001 DEPARTMENT OF CURRENCY MANAGEMENT, CENTRAL OFFICE, AMAR BUILDING, 4TH FLOOR, SIR P M ROAD,\nMUMBAI - 400001 फोन TELEPHONE No. 22663000 / 22604000\nई-मेल E-mail : cgmincdcm@rbi.org.in\nǑहन्दȣ आसान है, इसका प्रयोग बढ़ाइए",
