    {
      "logical_unit_id": "MD12809_lu25",
      "document_id": "MD12809",
      "title": "3.1 Reporting of Soiled Note Remittances to RBI",
      "text": "3.1 Reporting of Soiled Note Remittances to RBI\nSoiled note remittances to RBI shall not be shown as withdrawal by chest(s). In case such\nremittances to RBI are wrongly reported as 'withdrawals', a penalty of ₹50,000/- shall be\nlevied irrespective of the value of remittance and period of such wrong reporting.",
