    {
      "logical_unit_id": "MD12809_lu27",
      "document_id": "MD12809",
      "title": "Withdrawn",
      "text": "Withdrawn\nof different banks) have to be reported through 'Diversion Module' of CyM-CC Portal. The\nCC sending the diversion should initiate the entry. The receiving CC should acknowledge\nthe same. Diversions should not be reported as deposit / withdrawal. A penalty of\n₹50,000/- shall be levied for any such wrong reporting.",
